175
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:27,740
再試試一號區
Try zone one again.

176
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:33,960
該死，這是當務之急 我們必須馬上修復電力系統
Damn it! This is top priority.We gotta get these electrical systems on.

177
00:18:34,030 --> 00:18:36,860
沒有它 我們的整個安全系統就崩潰了
Our security program's loused up without them.

178
00:18:59,090 --> 00:19:00,420
別走，等著我
Don't go away.

179
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:20,930
道格，真沒想到會是你
Doug! Well, what a surprise!

180
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:26,610
你的那位電器天才在哪？
Where's that electrical genius of yours?

181
00:19:26,710 --> 00:19:30,170
我們打電話到他的辦公室 到處都找不到他
I called his office, the club, the marina. No luck.

182
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:31,720
他幹了什麼？
What's he done?

183
00:19:35,060 --> 00:19:36,550
過來，我給你倒杯喝的
Come on, I'll get you a drink.

184
00:19:39,390 --> 00:19:42,050
他一定幹了壞事 因為我爸爸打來電話了
He must've done something. My father called.

185
00:19:42,130 --> 00:19:44,390
他好多年都沒生過這麼大的氣了
He hasn't been that upset in years.

186
00:19:44,460 --> 00:19:46,190
知道他現在在哪？
Have any idea where he is?

187
00:19:48,870 --> 00:19:51,600
我丈夫的領地範圍非常大
Well my husband's territory ranges rather widely.

188
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:53,970
幾乎和大灰狼一樣
It's like that of the timber wolf,

189
00:19:54,040 --> 00:19:57,070
可能在方圓五十堨炙k的地方
anywhere within a 50-mile radius.

190
00:19:57,180 --> 00:19:59,410
不過，你要是願意等的話 他一會出現的
But if you wanna wait, he'll show up.

191
00:19:59,510 --> 00:20:01,500
一定的 他的衣服還在這呢
He has to. His clothes are here.

192
00:20:03,750 --> 00:20:06,450
- 給你倒杯酒，好嗎？ - 不，謝謝
-Can I get you a drink? -No, thanks.

193
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:11,150
看樣子你不想告訴我羅傑幹了些什麼
I guess you don't plan to tell me what Roger's done.

194
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:20,000
嗨，道格
Hi, Doug.

195
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:22,730
- 親愛的 - 嗨
-Honey. -Hello.

196
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:24,570
最近你喝什麼酒？
-What are you drinking these days?

197
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,330
我現在什麼也不喝
-Nothing, right now.

198
00:20:26,410 --> 00:20:30,000
歡迎從荒野歸來
Well, welcome back from the wilderness.

199
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:32,570
大駕當臨有何貴幹？
To what do we owe the pleasure?

200
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:35,050
卡拉罕測試一台備用電機
Callahan was testing a backup generator.

201
00:20:35,150 --> 00:20:37,640
忽然電流激增造成系統癱瘓
There was a systems failure.

202
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:42,350
- 怎麼會呢？ - 從理論上說不可能…
How can that be? It can't be, theoretically.

203
00:20:43,590 --> 00:20:46,990
除非你篡改了電路工程標準
Unless you screwed around with the electrical specifications.

204
00:20:48,830 --> 00:20:51,350
你倒是真不客氣？
That's being rather blunt, isn't it?

205
00:20:51,430 --> 00:20:53,090
說得沒錯
You betcha.

206
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:55,530
那麼別怪我也不客氣了
Then you'll understand my being equally blunt.

207
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:58,500
這與你有什麼狗屁關係？
What the hell business is it of yours?

208
00:20:58,570 --> 00:21:01,600
我只想知道你這麼做拿了多少回扣
I wonder what kickbacks were involved.

209
00:21:02,910 --> 00:21:05,430
我用不著在這媗尼琲獐o話
I don't have to take crap from you.

210
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:11,570
聽著，主倉庫現在起火
Listen. We had an electrical flare-up in the main utility room.

211
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:15,090
我認為所用的電線不符合我的要求
Some of that wiring wasn't exactly what I asked for.

212
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:18,960
我安裝在樓堛漕C根電線都很標準： 並且都經過檢查和批准
All the wire I put in is up to code, inspected and approved.

213
00:21:19,030 --> 00:21:22,960
那棟樓不能用普通標準 這你很清楚
Code's not enough for that building! And you know it!

214
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:26,060
所以我一再強調 所有材料都必須大大高於標準
I asked for installations way above standard.

215
00:21:26,130 --> 00:21:30,070
夥計，你生活在夢境 而我生活在現實中
Buddy, you live in a dream world. I deal in realities.

216
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:35,840
我要你的電路圖表和 所有派工單影本
I want your wiring diagrams and copies of your work orders.

217
00:21:35,910 --> 00:21:39,710
都找齊需要幾個星期 你還不夠資格讓我這麼做
That would take weeks and a lot more clout than you have!

218
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:41,970
送到我辦公室，明早9：00
In my office! Tomorrow, 9:00.

219
00:21:44,380 --> 00:21:47,820
人們說他曾在蒙大納和黑熊摔過跤
They say he used to wrestle grizzly bears in Montana.

220
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:52,990
當然是他年輕時 可能身體比現在壯
Of course, he was younger then. Probably in better condition.

221
00:21:56,030 --> 00:21:59,190
這件事一定讓你樂不可滋
You must have enjoyed all this immensely.

222
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:01,200
不，我沒有
No, I didn't.

223
00:22:01,270 --> 00:22:04,070
我真是為我們倆個人感到悲哀
Actually, I'm depressed for both of us.

224
00:22:04,140 --> 00:22:07,200
你希望我怎麼做 當頭給他一拳？
What did you expect me to do? Punch him in the nose?

225
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:13,310
你要是在爸爸的大樓堸竣F手腳 叫上帝去救你吧
If you've done anything to Dad's building, God help you.

226
00:22:13,380 --> 00:22:17,650
親愛的，我不需要乞求上帝 或是你的父親
Baby, I don't need God's help or your old man's. Not anymore.

227
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:20,650
不再需要了 所以別再指望老頭子一吼…
So don't expect me to shake every time Daddy barks...

228
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:24,950
我就會全身發抖 如果這是你希望的話
...even if that's what you want me to do.

229
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:29,360
我想要的 只是我當初想要嫁的那個人
All I want is the man I thought I married.

230
00:22:32,770 --> 00:22:36,930
我們繼續維持婚姻的理由 已經沒有了，是不是？
I guess we're running out of reasons to stay married, aren't we?

231
00:22:40,010 --> 00:22:43,910
天快黑了，出席晚會不能遲到
It's getting late.Mustn't miss the party.

