在我這個年齡？我只希望他們不會逃跑
At my age?I only care that they show up at all.

239
00:24:54,640 --> 00:24:56,400
沒那回事
Nonsense.

240
00:24:58,380 --> 00:25:00,440
乖乖別淘氣
Be a good girl, Elke.

241
00:25:00,510 --> 00:25:04,070
廚房媯鳩A留了牛奶 咱們回頭見
I left you some milk in the kitchen. See you later.

242
00:25:07,990 --> 00:25:11,550
- 找到西門斯了？ - 對，找到了
Did you find Simmons?Yeah, I found him.

243
00:25:11,620 --> 00:25:13,990
他到底改沒改過你的設計？
Did he or didn't he change your specs?

244
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:17,260
他沒有承認，但我敢打賭他幹了
He didn't admit it, but I bet you he did.

245
00:25:17,330 --> 00:25:20,300
他肯定是為了回扣才這麼幹的
Payoffs and kickbacks. The only way he could've swung it.

246
00:25:23,040 --> 00:25:25,470
你看
Here you are...

247
00:25:25,570 --> 00:25:27,600
這是你的原設計圖
...your original specs.

248
00:25:27,710 --> 00:25:30,340
只有一號區，我們總得從某處入手
Zone one only, but we gotta start somewhere.

249
00:25:33,810 --> 00:25:36,780
這個混蛋給我們出了一個天大的難題
That son of a bitch gave us an impossible job.

250
00:25:43,860 --> 00:25:46,790
- 蘇珊 - 你好，丹，真熱鬧
-Susan. -Hello, Dan.Good evening.

251
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:49,380
