253
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:53,760
你先到前面去
I'll meet you out front.

254
00:25:53,830 --> 00:25:56,130
我和蘇姍說幾句話
-I'd like to talk to Susan.

255
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:57,290
好的
-Right.

256
00:26:00,470 --> 00:26:02,960
能夠找到一個建築師，他設計了你
Find me the architect who designed you...

257
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:05,600
並且需要道格.羅伯茨？
...and who needs Doug Roberts?

258
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:06,800
我能
I do.

259
00:26:07,980 --> 00:26:10,780
女士們先生們，在這個歡慶的夜晚
Ladies and gentlemen, this is a gala evening.

260
00:26:10,850 --> 00:26:13,440
全城沉浸在節日喜慶氣氛中
The entire city is in a holiday mood.

261
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:16,820
