The list of luminaries reads like a Who's Who.

262
00:26:16,890 --> 00:26:19,480
其中有政府要員社交名流
There are leaders from society and government...

263
00:26:19,560 --> 00:26:22,760
電影電視明星
...stars of screen and television.

264
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:26,490
現在到達的是 尊敬的派克.加里參議員
And now, just arriving, the Honorable Gary Parker...

265
00:26:26,570 --> 00:26:29,800
聯邦政府城市改造委員會主席
...chairman of the Federal Urban Renewal Commission.

266
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:34,000
參議員專程從華盛頓趕來 參加今晚的落成儀式
The senator's in from Washington to be here for the dedication.

267
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:36,080
女士們先生們，歡迎派克參議員
Senator Parker, ladies and gentlemen.

268
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:39,740
我們請他到麥克風面前來 講幾句話
We'll try to get him to the microphone to say a few words for you.

269
00:26:39,810 --> 00:26:41,140
謝謝
Thank you.

270
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,480
謝謝
Thank you.

271
00:26:45,550 --> 00:26:47,780
謝謝.謝謝大家
Thank you. Thank you.

272
00:26:47,850 --> 00:26:50,350
謝謝了
Thank you very much.

273
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:52,790
今天晚上，我很榮幸
I'm honored to be here tonight.

274
00:26:52,860 --> 00:26:57,630
來到這個偉大的城市 紀念這次輝煌的標誌之後…
This magnificent building represents yet another landmark...

275
00:26:57,700 --> 00:27:00,960
這座宏偉的大廈將會成為 新的成功的里程牌
...in a long succession of landmarks for this great city.

276
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:02,330
他已經勝券在握了
I think you've got him in the bag, Jim.

277
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:06,530
謝謝你們讓我在這個 具有歷史意義的時刻親臨現場
--being here at this historic moment.

278
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,900
謝謝
Thank you.

279
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:13,700
謝謝
Thank you.

280
00:27:13,780 --> 00:27:17,680
女士們先生們 現在步入會場的西門斯先生和夫人
And now, ladies and gentlemen, Mr. and Mrs. Roger Simmons.

281
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:21,020
西門斯夫人是大廈建築商吉姆.鄧肯的女兒
Mrs. Simmons is the daughter of the builder, Jim Duncan.

282
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,890
你好嗎？
How are you?

283
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:32,020
你好，很高興見到你
Nice to see you, senator.

284
00:27:35,700 --> 00:27:37,500
你跑到哪去了？
Where were you all day?

285
00:27:37,600 --> 00:27:40,500
沒想到把我看得這麼緊
I wasn't aware the leash was that tight.

286
00:27:41,310 --> 00:27:44,300
等我有了空，我要問你幾個問題
Later, I wanna ask you a few questions...

287
00:27:44,410 --> 00:27:46,900
必須如實的回答
...and I expect some straight answers.

288
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:52,420
女士們先生們 羅伯特.拉姆齊市長和夫人到
And now, ladies and gentlemen, Mayor and Mrs. Robert Ramsay.

289
00:28:18,780 --> 00:28:20,410
謝謝，非常感謝
I thank you very much.

290
00:28:24,720 --> 00:28:28,880
我很榮幸為這棟摩天大樓的落成剪綵…
I hereby dedicate this magnificent glass tower...

291
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:31,750
它是世界上最高的建築
...tallest building in the world!

292
00:28:38,830 --> 00:28:40,320
我能做到
We'll make it.

293
00:28:40,370 --> 00:28:42,130
好了
That's it.

294
00:28:46,770 --> 00:28:48,360
好了嗎，卡拉罕？
All right, Callahan?

295
00:28:49,910 --> 00:28:51,210
開燈
Hit them.

296
