Come on, Dan.

300
00:29:39,130 --> 00:29:42,060
我先去趟辦公室 過一會再上來
I'm going by the office. I'll be up in a few minutes.

301
00:29:58,240 --> 00:30:00,410
這奡漲滮茯了.那是京門大橋吧
I've never seen the bridge look like that.

302
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:04,380
- 這真是太漂亮了！ - 簡直令人難以置信！
-It's unbelievable! -Astonishing!

303
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,090
下面怎麼樣，比格洛先生？
-How did it go down there, Mr. Bigelow?

304
00:30:21,170 --> 00:30:23,530
- 很好，謝謝，晚安 - 晚安
-Fine, thank you. Good night.

305
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:25,730
要不要留一條夜急專線？
Shall I leave you a night line?

306
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:28,400
不用了，白天電話已經接過了 全部切斷吧
No, you can disconnect. I've had it with phones for today.

307
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:30,240
- 晚安 - 晚安
Good night. Good night.

