00:33:18,310 --> 00:33:21,140
把你藏在下面的東西拿給參議員吧
Show him what you've been hiding back there.

336
00:33:21,210 --> 00:33:22,700
好的，先生
Yes, sir.

337
00:33:27,850 --> 00:33:29,340
29年的藏酒！
1929?

338
00:33:29,420 --> 00:33:31,510
今晚你只喝這種酒
-That's all you'll drink tonight.

339
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:32,850
一整箱嗎？
-A whole case?

340
00:33:32,930 --> 00:33:35,760
喝剩下的，我們給你運回華盛頓去
What you don't drink, we'll ship to Washington.

341
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:37,960
- 請打開一瓶，好吧 - 好的，先生
-Open a bottle, will you? -Yes, sir.

342
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:43,660
你是從哪兒搞到這種酒的？
How did you ever come by a whole case?

343
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,830
告訴我，吉姆
Come on, Jim.

344
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:48,160
這算不了什麼
It's nothing.

345
00:33:55,310 --> 00:33:57,650
我猜： 你在找一個人？
I guess you're looking for someone.

346
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:58,940
你看見他了？
I am. Have you seen him?

347
00:33:59,020 --> 00:34:01,650
我為帕提和我要了杯酒 你想要點什麼？
I've ordered for Patty. What can I get you?

348
00:34:01,720 --> 00:34:03,280
現在不喝，謝謝，羅傑
-Nothing right now. Thank you, Roger.

349
00:34:03,360 --> 00:34:08,290
蘇珊，告訴我，當丈夫決定要離開兩年…
-Susan, tell me,What does a girl do in San Francisco

350
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:11,490
那姑娘在三藩市幹些什麼？
when her old man decides to leave for two years?

351
00:34:14,730 --> 00:34:16,460
我不知道
Beats me, buddy.

352
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:18,530
不想找個男朋友？
No headhunting?

353
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:21,200
幹這種事會有點困難
I've had a little trouble making that work.

354
00:34:21,310 --> 00:34:23,970
要不咱們談談，明天的午餐？
Could we discuss that tomorrow at lunch?

355
00:34:24,040 --> 00:34:25,340
不
No.

356
00:34:34,690 --> 00:34:36,550
你想念你的別墅嗎
-You must miss your villa.

357
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:38,280
也想也不想
-Well, yes and no.

358
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:41,190
法國南方令人氣味索然
It gets rather dull in the south of France.

359
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:44,130
我說的是真的，除了游泳，開快艇
Nothing but swimming and yachting

360
00:34:44,200 --> 00:34:46,030
就是沒完沒了的晚會
partying and all that sort of thing.

361
00:34:46,100 --> 00:34:51,370
說來你也許不信 她們為了幾個不多的單身漢爭風吃醋
And believe it or not, they fight over the few eligible bachelors.

362
00:34:51,470 --> 00:34:53,960
包括我這樣的老廢物
Even such old scraps as l.

363
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:56,740
- 你不要這樣謙卑吧 - 請坐？
-No false humility, please. -Oh, shall we?

364
00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:00,430
我…
I. .

365
00:35:00,510 --> 00:35:04,000
我決定回到三藩市的現實生活中來…
I decided to come back to the reality of San Francisco.

366
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:07,520
恢復我的判斷力和謙虛謹慎…
...to regain my perspective and my humility...

367
00:35:07,590 --> 00:35:10,990
而且多花點時間在我唯一擅長的事情上
...and spend more time at the one thing I'm really good at:

368
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:13,020
股票市場
The stock market.

369
00:35:13,090 --> 00:35:17,190
你是說蒙特卡洛的損失 三藩市的收穫
Monte Carlo's losses, San Francisco's gains.

370
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:18,860
謝謝
Thank you.

371
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:23,130
你… 你相信不相信命運?？
Do you believe in destiny?

372
00:35:25,140 --> 00:35:27,200
所有的好事，我都相信
I believe in all good things.

373
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:33,510
我回家的一個重要的原因
There must be a reason for my coming back home.

374
00:35:34,950 --> 00:35:36,380
和你相會
Meeting you.

375
00:35:56,700 --> 00:35:58,430
肯定有問題
This can't be right.

376
00:36:04,740 --> 00:36:08,140
電線燙手，最好馬上關掉
It's too hot.You better leave it off.

377
00:36:18,690 --> 00:36:20,390
控制室，韋斯
Utility. Wes.

378
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:23,690
我是道格，我和威爾在83樓 這堛犒q線有問題
Doug, I'm up on 83 with Will.We got a wiring problem.

379
00:36:23,760 --> 00:36:25,750
這堛犒q線有問題 如果超載會有大麻煩的
Overloads could be trouble.

380
00:36:25,830 --> 00:36:28,960
你盡可能多的關閉一號區系統的電力
Shut down as many of the zone one systems as you can.

381
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:33,160
我不能這麼做.為了落成儀式 我們打開了所有的燈
I can't do that.All the lights are on for the dedication ceremony.

382
00:36:33,270 --> 00:36:36,770
所有的 你是說，整個大樓？
You mean the whole building?

383
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:39,570
我們這堣@切正常
We're taking the overload just fine.

384
00:36:39,650 --> 00:36:42,670
打燈關掉，馬上關掉
Well, shut it down right away.

385
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:46,210
沒有鄧肯先生的直接批准 我不能這麼做
I can't do that without an okay from Mr. Duncan himself.

386
00:36:46,290 --> 00:36:49,690
一切責任由我來負 你馬上關掉那該死的燈
I'll accept the responsibility. Just turn off the lights!

387
00:36:49,760 --> 00:36:52,450
那舞會怎麼辦？
What about the lights in the tower for the party?

388
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:55,220
我沒有說關掉所有的燈 只說關掉超載的燈
-Not all the power, just the overload!

389
00:36:55,290 --> 00:36:56,260
好的，先生
-Yes, sir, Mr. Roberts!

390
00:36:57,500 --> 00:37:00,800
我們馬上到81樓檢查繼電器
We better get down to 81 and check the relay systems.

391
00:37:00,870 --> 00:37:02,930
他們把全樓的燈都打開了
They turned on everything in the whole building.

392
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:05,730
81樓有問題
There's something on 81.

393
00:37:19,890 --> 00:37:24,080
比爾給消防隊打電話 以防自動報警線失靈
Phone it in, in case the lines to the fire department are out.

394
00:37:24,160 --> 00:37:26,450
- 我去81樓 - 好的
-I'll be in 81. -You got it.

395
00:38:48,210 --> 00:38:49,830
把窗簾扯下來！
Get those drapes!

396
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:57,310
把火壓滅！ 快把火壓滅！
Smother it! Try to smother it!

397
00:38:57,380 --> 00:39:00,180
把它包住 把他全包住！快，快！
Pull it around over here. Put it all over him. Come on!

398
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:03,120
往火上澆水！
Let's get some water onto that fire.

399
00:39:05,220 --> 00:39:06,710
打開水龍頭！
Turn it on!

400
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:10,890
上帝
God

401
00:39:31,850 --> 00:39:33,840
往下，往下一點
Down, down! Stay low!

402
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:41,120
快點去叫輛救護車
Call an ambulance for this man.

403
00:39:42,530 --> 00:39:44,720
快點！ 叫輛救護車！
Get on the ball! Call an ambulance!

404
00:39:46,030 --> 00:39:47,690
叫這個樓層的人馬上撤離
I want everybody off this floor!

405
00:39:47,770 --> 00:39:50,200
- 消防隊呢？ - 他們馬上就到
-The fire department? -On their way.

406
00:39:50,270 --> 00:39:53,400
叫救護車！ 幫我一下，把他送上電梯
Get that ambulance. Give me a hand. Get him in the elevator.

407
00:39:53,510 --> 00:39:57,870
儘量不要用手碰他 抓住他的皮帶
All right, try not to touch him. Try to get him by his belt.

408
00:39:57,940 --> 00:39:59,880
我在81樓 這堨X事故了
This is 81.

409
00:39:59,950 --> 00:40:02,180
一個人被燒傷了，叫輛救護車
A man's been burned. Get an ambulance.

410
00:40:02,250 --> 00:40:05,770
- 是的，馬上 - 給頂層的鄧肯打電話
Yes, right away.Call Duncan in the tower.

411
00:40:05,850 --> 00:40:07,790
上面有很多的人
He's got a lot of people up there.

412
00:40:07,850 --> 00:40:09,550
- 什麼？ - 快打電話！
-What? -Do it now!

413
00:40:26,370 --> 00:40:28,030
是羅伯茨先生
It's Mr. Roberts.

414
00:40:28,140 --> 00:40:31,010
是我，道格，我們開始擔心你啦
Yeah, Doug. We were getting worried about you.

415
00:40:31,080 --> 00:40:34,340
蘇姍在這，派克參議員 市長還有市長夫人
Susan's here, Senator Parker, the mayor and his wife.

416
00:40:34,410 --> 00:40:37,940
他們都想知道世界上最好的建築師在哪
They're asking why the greatest architect isn't here.

417
00:40:38,020 --> 00:40:41,350
別管這個了.威爾.吉丁斯被燒傷了 傷勢很嚴重
Never mind that. Will Giddings has been badly burned.

418
00:40:41,420 --> 00:40:44,320
威爾燒傷了？怎麼搞的？
Will Giddings burned? How?

419
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:46,290
我已經叫了救護車
An ambulance is coming,

420
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:50,290
現在最好考慮一下 把上面那些人帶到一層去
but you better think about getting those people down on the ground floor.

421
00:40:50,360 --> 00:40:52,890
為什麼？ 這堶接菑鶪F！
What for? We got a fire here!

422
00:40:54,370 --> 00:40:57,130
我想已經控制住了，可是
Well, I think it's under control, but--

423
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:59,800
那麼，你還瞎緊張什麼？
Well, then why the urgency?

424
00:40:59,910 --> 00:41:01,770
瞎緊張？
Urgency?

425
00:41:01,840 --> 00:41:05,000
鄧肯，我告訴你，如果這是由電線引起的
If fluky wiring in this building caused that fire...

426
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:07,480
那麼任何地方都可能起火
...fires could break out everywhere!

427
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:10,980
道格，我看你是有點小題大作了
Doug, I think you're overreacting.

428
00:41:11,050 --> 00:41:12,850
威爾.吉丁斯受傷，我很難過
I feel sorry for Will Giddings,

429
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:15,220
我們會照顧他的
but he'll be taken care of.

430
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:17,780
81樓主倉庫著火
But I won't concern myself

431
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:19,980
我不擔心
with a fire in a storage room on 81 ...

432
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:22,690
因為它不可能影響到我這
...because it can't possibly affect us up here...

433
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:24,190
在這棟大樓堙A這是不可能的
...not in this building.

434
00:41:25,560 --> 00:41:29,690
等消防隊到來這後 你馬上派人來通知我
Now, have someone call me when the fire department arrives.

435
00:41:29,770 --> 00:41:32,900
現在你馬上換上禮服 上來參加晚會
Meanwhile, get in your dinner jacket and come up and join the party!

436
00:41:33,010 --> 00:41:34,370
現在，快點！
Now come on!

437
00:42:07,170 --> 00:42:10,610
你知道蒙哥馬利街角的是哪棟樓…
What building's on the corner of Montgomery and--

438
00:42:12,780 --> 00:42:14,510
天?
Oh, Jesus!

439
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:18,210
- 是摩天大樓 - 什麼？
-The glass tower! -What?

440
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:20,080
摩天大樓！
The glass tower!

441
00:42:21,950 --> 00:42:24,680
但願著火的是一樓
I sure hope that fire's on the first floor.

442
00:42:27,390 --> 00:42:30,090
你參加過高樓滅火嗎？
Did you ever fight one in a high rise?

443
00:42:30,160 --> 00:42:31,250
是的
Yeah

444
00:42:34,600 --> 00:42:36,620
有那麼困難嗎？
Is it as rough as I hear?

445
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:41,260
就像在煙囪媟壑
Like being inside a chimney.

446
00:43:02,830 --> 00:43:04,060
我的天?！
Jesus!

447
00:43:04,130 --> 00:43:06,690
這些人比我們先到
How in the hell did they get here before we did?

448
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:11,160
現在沒人待在家堣F吧？
Don't anybody ever stay home anymore?

449
00:43:28,620 --> 00:43:32,060
- 來幾個幫幫忙到那邊去 - 是

450
00:43:32,120 --> 00:43:34,680
你知道我讓你到那邊去？

451
00:43:34,760 --> 00:43:37,060
邁克，著火了，煙很大
-Mike, she's throwing a lot of smoke.

452
00:43:37,130 --> 00:43:38,760
- 81樓，是嗎？ - 是的
-Eighty-first floor, right?

453
00:43:38,830 --> 00:43:41,130
我們控制了大堂 發出了第二次警報
We've got lobby control, second alarm is in.

454
00:43:41,200 --> 00:43:43,690
- 組織臨時指揮部 - 知道了
-Set up a Forward Command. -Got it.

455
00:43:46,440 --> 00:43:50,240
- 隊長，這是羅伯茨建築師
Chief this is Roberts, the architect.

456
00:43:50,310 --> 00:43:51,610
情況怎麼樣，卡菲？
-What do we got here, Kappy?

457
00:43:51,680 --> 00:43:54,770
據我們瞭解 火是從81樓燒起來的 主倉庫情況很糟
-Fire started, 81 st floor, storage room.

458
00:43:54,850 --> 00:43:58,650
產生大量濃煙 我們看不清楚火勢蔓延多遠
It's bad. Smoke's so thick, we can't tell how far it's spread.

459
00:43:58,720 --> 00:44:00,150
你們的通風系統呢？
-Exhaust system?

460
00:44:00,220 --> 00:44:03,090
它們應該反向自動排煙 一定是電機被燒毀了
Should've reversed automatically. It must be a motor burnout.

461
00:44:03,160 --> 00:44:06,090
- 噴連系統呢？ - 在81層沒人啟動
-Sprinklers? -They're not working on 81.

462
00:44:06,960 --> 00:44:08,930
- 為什麼？ - 我不知道
-Why not? -I don't know.

463
00:44:11,100 --> 00:44:12,530
- 吉姆？ - 我在這
-Jim? -Yes, sir?

464
00:44:12,600 --> 00:44:15,530
簡要描敘一下你們的水塔系統
Give us a quick refresher on your standpipe system.

465
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:18,660
每層都有出水口  3英寸和1.5英寸兩種水管
-Floors have 3 and 1.5-inch outlets.

466
00:44:18,770 --> 00:44:19,790
水流量？
-GPM?

467
00:44:19,910 --> 00:44:23,670
1到68層每分鐘1500加侖 68到100層是1000加侖
Fifteen hundred from ground to 68, 1,000 from 68 to 100...

468
00:44:23,740 --> 00:44:25,680
再往上是500加侖
...and 500 from there to the roof.

469
00:44:25,780 --> 00:44:28,680
你肯定這些電梯是按緊急狀態設置的？
Are these elevators programmed for emergencies?

470
00:44:28,750 --> 00:44:30,980
- 這兩層是 - 你的設計圖放在幾樓？
-What floor are your plans on?

471
00:44:31,050 --> 00:44:32,410
79樓，我的辦公室
-79. My office.

472
00:44:32,480 --> 00:44:36,250
很好，離火災低兩層 把臨時指揮部設在那
That's two floors below the fire. It'll be our Forward Command.

473
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:39,190
好了，夥計們，拿上設備 我們上去
Men, take up the equipment.Let's go.

474
00:44:41,560 --> 00:44:42,860
好的
Okey

475
00:44:46,160 --> 00:44:50,260
- 你們這些建築師啊 - 對，都是我們的錯
Architects!Yeah, it's all our fault.

476
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:55,940
你們明明知道對七層樓以上 的火災我們沒有把握
You know we can't fight a fire in anything over the 7th floor.

477
00:44:56,010 --> 00:44:59,640
可你們還是能蓋多高就蓋多高
But you keep building them as high as you can.

478
00:44:59,710 --> 00:45:03,080
你是來滅火的，還是來滅我的？
Are you here to take me on, or the fire?

479
00:45:05,150 --> 00:45:08,380
好的，81樓情況怎麼樣？ 所有的人都撤退了嗎？
What about the 81st floor? You got everybody out of there?

480
00:45:10,820 --> 00:45:13,310
我要看所有設計圖 81到85樓
I wanna see all floor plans, 81 through 85.

481
00:45:13,390 --> 00:45:14,880
沒問題
Gotcha.

482
00:45:14,930 --> 00:45:18,190
這些衡梁和玻璃正是我擔心的
This is what worries me. Those beams and that glass.

483
00:45:18,260 --> 00:45:22,200
隊長，81樓的房客已經撤走了 但那的情況不妙
Chief, 81 has been evacuated, but it doesn't look too good up there.

484
00:45:22,270 --> 00:45:24,390
給我一份承租人名單要多長時間
Give me a list of your tenants.

485
00:45:24,470 --> 00:45:26,730
不要擔心他們 我們正要幫他們撤離
Don't worry. We're moving them out now.

486
00:45:26,840 --> 00:45:28,500
不是住戶，是商業房客
Not live-ins. Businesses.

487
00:45:28,610 --> 00:45:31,470
這方面我們很幸運 大部份都沒有搬來
We lucked up. Most of them haven't moved in yet.

488
00:45:31,540 --> 00:45:33,480
已經搬進來的今天也不辦公
Those that have are off at night.

489
00:45:33,580 --> 00:45:36,140
我想知道他們是誰，我不管他們在哪
I wanna know who they are, not where.

490
00:45:36,210 --> 00:45:39,310
就是知道了他們是誰 又能怎麼樣呢？
What's that got to do with anything? Who they are?

491
00:45:39,380 --> 00:45:41,980
他們當中有沒有羊毛或是絲綢製造商？
Any wool or silk manufacturers?

492
00:45:42,050 --> 00:45:44,890
要知道著火會使羊毛和線綢散發氰化物
In a fire, wool and silk give off cyanide gas.

493
00:45:44,960 --> 00:45:47,080
你們當中有沒有體育用品製造商？
Any sporting-good manufacturers, like table-tennis balls?

494
00:45:47,160 --> 00:45:49,820
例如乒乓球會散發毒氣
They give off toxic gases.

495
00:45:49,900 --> 00:45:54,090
