845
01:25:47,800 --> 01:25:48,960
我馬上下達命令
Right away.

846
01:25:49,030 --> 01:25:52,260
我想挨著你的指揮部建立指揮中心 可以嗎
Our communications will be near the Forward Command center.

847
01:25:52,340 --> 01:25:55,200
不，太危險了 離電梯遠點
No, too dangerous. Stay out of those elevators.

848
01:25:55,310 --> 01:25:57,570
那好，先生，我們只好從樓梯跑上去
Then, sir, we'll just trot up the stairs.

849
01:25:57,680 --> 01:26:00,610
那你就跑79層吧
You'll just trot right up to 79, huh?

850
01:26:00,680 --> 01:26:03,810
- 我們在大堂待命，先生 - 謝謝
Standing by in the lobby.Thank you.

851
01:26:32,580 --> 01:26:35,070
該死的.
This ain't gonna help any!

852
01:26:41,120 --> 01:26:44,210
他們聽不到我們 堶惘300個人
They won't hear us in there. There's 300 people!

853
01:26:44,290 --> 01:26:47,280
這個防火門厚2英尺半
It's a fire door. It's over 2.5 inches thick.

854
01:26:48,930 --> 01:26:53,630
- 也許我們可以從空調管道下去 - 我們能不能跟著你？
I could crawl through the duct.Will we be able to go with you?

855
01:26:53,700 --> 01:26:57,760
那要經過一個豎井 直接從135樓到頂層
That leads to a pipe shaft that's 135 floors straight down.

856
01:26:59,400 --> 01:27:00,960
用這個
This

857
01:27:01,640 --> 01:27:04,040
菲力浦，你要好好照顧兩位女士
Phillip, take care of these ladies.

858
01:27:04,110 --> 01:27:06,240
你要對她們付責任
They're your responsibility now.

859
01:28:17,310 --> 01:28:18,710
好的，等一下
All right, I'll tell him.

860
01:28:20,550 --> 01:28:22,710
- 隊長？ - 65樓怎麼樣？
-How is it on 65?

861
01:28:22,790 --> 01:28:25,690
- 他們正在控制 - 下面仍然有火
-They're containing it. Well, it's still below us.

862
01:28:25,760 --> 01:28:28,880
我們去看看 注意小心電線
Let's take a look. Okay, watch the electrics.

863
01:28:48,110 --> 01:28:49,550
過來
Come here!

864
01:28:50,650 --> 01:28:54,340
發電機燒了 備用機應該啟動了
The master generator's blown.The backup should've kicked on.

865
01:28:54,420 --> 01:28:56,650
看看怎麼還沒有動靜
See what's holding up our starters.

866
01:29:08,900 --> 01:29:10,300
怎麼回事
What happened?

867
01:29:15,140 --> 01:29:17,040
我們到底在哪
Where the hell are we?

868
01:29:25,820 --> 01:29:27,880
- 推呀！ - 我在推

869
01:29:33,390 --> 01:29:36,220
保安部，我是鄧肯 是主發電機停了嗎
Security, this is Duncan. Have the main breakers gone?

870
01:29:39,830 --> 01:29:41,700
整個系統癱瘓了
The whole system's failed.

871
01:29:41,770 --> 01:29:44,560
知道來這的消防隊走到哪了
What's the last report on the firemen getting here?

872
01:29:45,840 --> 01:29:47,330
快到了
Are they on their way?

873
01:29:49,940 --> 01:29:51,640
等等
Hold on to me a second.

874
01:30:31,680 --> 01:30:33,050
等等
Hold on!

875
01:30:37,720 --> 01:30:41,050
- 天哪，那是我們的人！ - 哦，天哪
Christ! That's one of our men!Oh, God!

876
01:30:41,760 --> 01:30:45,490
好，我們順著繩子爬下去
Go down by rope.

877
01:30:45,560 --> 01:30:47,260
注意安全
Better get it.

878
01:30:47,330 --> 01:30:48,630
長官
Sir?

879
01:30:48,700 --> 01:30:52,160
我們得把它修好 下到65層跳到電梯頂上
We'll rappel down to 65 and use the top of that elevator

880
01:30:52,240 --> 01:30:53,760
我們從那出去
as an exit.

881
01:30:53,840 --> 01:30:56,030
不能試著把這門打開嗎
Why not pry open the doors at this level?

882
01:30:57,640 --> 01:30:59,910
我看不行
I don't think so.

883
01:30:59,980 --> 01:31:03,710
我不行，我會掉下去的
I can't make it.I'll fall. I know I'll fall.

884
01:31:06,150 --> 01:31:09,520
那好，你第一個下
Then you better go first.

885
01:31:09,590 --> 01:31:12,780
這樣你掉下去 就不會帶上我們
That way, when you fall, you won't take any of us with you.

886
01:31:25,500 --> 01:31:27,090
開始吧
Let's go to work.

887
01:31:37,650 --> 01:31:39,580
檢查那邊的走廊
Check all rooms in that corridor.

888
01:31:40,980 --> 01:31:42,420
把這邊的房間門打開
Check this room.

889
01:31:47,690 --> 01:31:49,060
把它踢開
Tear it down.

890
01:32:49,320 --> 01:32:51,690
看，和學校上訓練課教的一樣
See? Just like we taught you in training.

891
01:32:53,790 --> 01:32:55,520
來，把它打開
Open it up.

892
01:33:06,300 --> 01:33:08,500
我聽見了，我明白
Of course I read you!

893
01:33:08,570 --> 01:33:11,770
我現在不知道他在哪 如果看見他 我會轉告他的
I don't know where he is, but if I see him, I'll tell him.

894
01:33:13,740 --> 01:33:16,240
投入火海 比逃離火海容易的多
-Must be an easier way to get to a fire.

895
01:33:16,310 --> 01:33:18,870
- 對我們不是 - 邁克，你跑哪去了
-Not for us. -Where've you been?

896
01:33:18,980 --> 01:33:20,710
來的路上遇到了點小麻煩
-We had trouble getting here.

897
01:33:20,780 --> 01:33:23,080
海軍飛行指揮官需要你馬上到大堂去
The Navy flight commander needs you.

898
01:33:23,150 --> 01:33:25,120
65樓，要我走下去
Just walk 65 floors down?

899
01:33:25,220 --> 01:33:28,250
只要走五樓 你就可以到60樓用輔助電梯
Only five. A freight elevator on 60's running auxiliary power.

900
01:33:28,330 --> 01:33:31,020
- 你能控制嗎？ - 我看沒問題
-Got it controlled? -Getting there.

901
01:33:31,090 --> 01:33:34,550
很好，你們留在這 告訴他我一會就到
You men stay here with the chief. Tell him I'm on my way.

902
01:33:34,630 --> 01:33:36,260
哦，邁克…
Oh, Mike... .

903
01:33:37,130 --> 01:33:38,620
這是你的人嗎
This one of your men?

904
01:33:40,840 --> 01:33:43,860
丹.比奇洛，不是消防隊員
"Dan Bigelow. " Nope.Must be a civilian.

905
01:33:51,050 --> 01:33:53,380
奧霍羅漢他馬上就到
Okay to O'Hallorhan. He's on his way.

906
01:34:20,180 --> 01:34:23,040
- 你看！ - 那兒還有一架！
Look!There's another one there!

907
01:34:51,140 --> 01:34:53,170
卡洛斯，電話給我，好嗎
Carlos, give me that security phone, will you?

908
01:34:53,240 --> 01:34:57,610
- 羅伯茨先生，你怎麼上來了？ - 以後再跟你說吧
How'd you get in here?I'll give it to you later.

909
01:34:58,850 --> 01:35:02,340
幫我接奧霍羅漢 沒關係，找誰都得
Give me O'Hallorhan.Anybody'll do.

910
01:35:02,450 --> 01:35:06,250
聽著，南面南區的通道被堵死了 是水泥
Listen, the south stairwell is blocked. Cement, for chrissake!

911
01:35:06,320 --> 01:35:08,590
你能不能派人上來把它打開？
Can you send somebody up to break it loose?

912
01:35:10,390 --> 01:35:12,020
已經派人上來了？ 怎麼
They're on their way? How--?

913
01:35:13,900 --> 01:35:14,860
好吧
Okey

914
01:35:15,600 --> 01:35:18,260
糟了，艾爾卡
Oh, my Lord, Elke.

915
01:35:18,340 --> 01:35:22,000
可憐的小貓，它還在公寓堜O
My poor cat.She's still in the apartment.

916
01:35:22,070 --> 01:35:24,560
不要緊，火不會燒到那
I'm sure the fire didn't get up that high yet.

917
01:35:24,640 --> 01:35:26,670
它一定會沒事的
She'll be all right.

918
01:35:32,980 --> 01:35:35,040
- 你們好 - 你好
-Hello, ma'am. -Hello.

919
01:35:35,150 --> 01:35:38,120
- 你們怎麼樣啊？ - 很好，見到你們很高興
-How're you doing? -We're fine. Glad to see you.

920
01:35:38,220 --> 01:35:40,950
就是那扇門，它被水泥封死了
That's the door right there. It's blocked with cement.

921
01:35:41,020 --> 01:35:42,080
好
Ok

922
01:35:51,200 --> 01:35:54,500
我們就去把那玩意兒炸掉
We're gonna have to blow that thing.

923
01:35:59,680 --> 01:36:03,540
- 米爾勒夫人？ - 是羅伯茨先生
Mrs. Mueller?It's Mr. Roberts!

924
01:36:05,850 --> 01:36:07,780
米爾勒夫人
Mrs. Mueller! Phillip!

925
01:36:07,850 --> 01:36:11,480
聽見了！ 我們要把這扇門炸開！
We hear you. We're gonna blow this door.

926
01:36:11,560 --> 01:36:13,420
讓所有的人躲開
Get everybody clear.

927
01:36:13,490 --> 01:36:16,320
你只有30秒鐘，明白嗎？
You've got about 30 seconds. Understood?

928
01:36:18,660 --> 01:36:20,190
明白了
Understood!

929
01:36:24,530 --> 01:36:27,300
好的，夫人，我們到下面躲一躲
Okay, ma'am, let's get down there. Out of the way.

930
01:36:29,570 --> 01:36:32,300
請大家離這遠一點 他們就要炸這扇門了
Please go back. They're gonna dynamite this door.

931
01:36:32,380 --> 01:36:35,070
後退，我們就要炸門了
Step back, please. We're blowing the door.

932
01:36:37,310 --> 01:36:38,750
好的，蹲著
Okay, get down low.

933
01:36:45,120 --> 01:36:47,020
你們用什麼炸藥？
-What kind of explosives are you using?

934
01:36:47,090 --> 01:36:50,650
是塑膠炸藥.C- 4. 能把任何東西炸個洞
-It's plastic C-4. Blow a hole in anything.

935
01:37:02,670 --> 01:37:05,330
來，把這個照亮
Here, shine this on the bag for me.

936
01:37:07,110 --> 01:37:08,940
好的，放到那邊
That's it. Keep it up here.

937
01:37:11,980 --> 01:37:15,750
- 是不是會?的一聲？ - 不用擔心，孩子
Is there gonna be a bang?Nothing for you to worry about, baby.

938
01:37:15,820 --> 01:37:17,250
你會很安全的
You'll be safe.

939
01:37:20,420 --> 01:37:22,390
都準備好了嗎？
Okay, everybody ready?

940
01:37:40,740 --> 01:37:43,140
快走，夥計們
Good going, Brian.

941
01:37:43,250 --> 01:37:44,910
嗨
Hey

942
01:37:46,420 --> 01:37:47,910
你沒事吧？
You all right?

943
01:37:58,800 --> 01:38:01,730
我是詹姆士.鄧肯. 我們能不能從這下去？
I'm James Duncan. Can we get down that way?

944
01:38:01,830 --> 01:38:04,890
沒希望了，先生.樓梯全被炸毀了
No, not a chance, sir. The stairway below is completely gone.

945
01:38:23,050 --> 01:38:25,020
女士們先生們，聽我說
Everyone, listen!

946
01:38:25,090 --> 01:38:27,250
大家安靜下來 聽我說
-Hold it down! -Listen!

947
01:38:29,060 --> 01:38:31,150
情況是這樣的 消防部門通知我說…
I've been informed that there's no possibility...

948
01:38:31,260 --> 01:38:35,060
我們不能從樓梯口下去
...of using this stairway to get out.

949
01:38:36,400 --> 01:38:37,960
我，非常抱歉
Now, I'm sorry.

950
01:38:42,110 --> 01:38:46,470
帕提！我們還有希望離開這
Patty!There's still a chance we can get out of here.

951
01:38:47,480 --> 01:38:50,810
你沒有聽見我爸爸說的話？ 這條路走不通
Didn't you hear what my father said? You can't get out that way.

952
01:38:50,880 --> 01:38:53,710
你到底跟不跟我走？
Are you coming or not?

953
01:38:56,050 --> 01:38:57,110
不
No

954
01:38:59,720 --> 01:39:02,850
如果你想得到批准再逃命的話 隨你的便
If you have to wait for permission to save your own life, go ahead.

955
01:39:04,330 --> 01:39:06,060
- 我要走 - 羅傑，你…
-I'm getting out. -Roger, you... .

956
01:39:11,970 --> 01:39:14,700
我們就快要死了

957
01:39:43,900 --> 01:39:46,270
快！快！
Come on!Come on!

958
01:39:48,240 --> 01:39:51,110
我們到那邊去 你們倆負責頂棚
Let's go. You guys, hose the ceiling.

959
01:39:52,680 --> 01:39:54,300
你倆，到那堶悼h！
You two, in there!

960
01:39:59,980 --> 01:40:01,950
我猜你准以為我會失約
-I guess you thought I stood you up.

961
01:40:02,020 --> 01:40:03,920
有過這念頭
-It crossed my mind.

962
01:40:05,460 --> 01:40:07,550
- 你真的沒事嗎？
You sure you're all right?

963
01:40:09,830 --> 01:40:13,850
道格，那些直升機  它們能救我們出去，是嗎？
Those helicopters, they'll get us out of here, won't they?

964
01:40:13,960 --> 01:40:16,230
如果風不太大的話
Sure they will if there's not too much wind.

965
01:40:18,170 --> 01:40:19,570
一部份人
Some party.

966
01:40:21,370 --> 01:40:22,600
道格…
Nuge

967
01:40:28,280 --> 01:40:31,980
你們還想要點什麼？
Can I get you anything else?

968
01:40:32,050 --> 01:40:33,450
不要？
No

969
01:40:56,940 --> 01:40:58,170
該死的！
Damn

970
01:41:02,710 --> 01:41:07,120
直升機已經準備好了 但是樓頂的強風加大了降落的危險性
The choppers are here, but the winds make a landing attempt too risky.

971
01:41:07,180 --> 01:41:09,850
還能抽幾個人嗎 讓他們到皮爾斯大廈樓頂
Get some men on top of the Peerless Building...

972
01:41:09,920 --> 01:41:12,620
我想在那兒安個吊索 直達樓頂舞廳
...and get a breeches buoy to the Promenade Room.

973
01:41:12,690 --> 01:41:15,210
風這麼大，我們無法把繩索射上去
We can't shoot a line that far in this wind.

974
01:41:15,290 --> 01:41:18,990
- 從升直機上射也不行嗎 - 我馬上去準備
Why not shoot it from a chopper?I'll get right on it.

975
01:41:22,500 --> 01:41:23,520
鄧？
-Doc?

976
01:41:23,630 --> 01:41:25,460
隊長，他被天花板壓在身上
-Chief, the ceiling fell in on him.

977
01:41:25,540 --> 01:41:28,470
找到他的時候，他被埋在熱海中
By the time I got to him, he was covered with hot stuff.

978
01:41:54,430 --> 01:41:57,060
我真夠丟人現眼的？
Pretty ridiculous spectacle, right?

979
01:41:58,000 --> 01:42:00,870
- 那兒根本下不去 - 謝天謝地，你沒事
-There's no way down. -Thank God you're all right.

980
01:42:02,440 --> 01:42:06,600
- 我們該怎麼辦啊？ - 我知道我該怎麼辦
-Oh, Roger, what are we gonna go? -I know what I'm gonna do.

981
01:42:06,680 --> 01:42:08,580
喝個大醉
Get quietly drunk.

982
01:42:11,380 --> 01:42:14,910
如果你該對此負責任 我知道你的感覺
If you're responsible for this, I know what you must be feeling.

983
01:42:14,980 --> 01:42:17,680
你不懂那個詞的含義
You don't know the meaning of the word.

984
01:42:17,750 --> 01:42:19,310
- 負責任？ - 感覺！
-Responsible? -Feeling!

985
01:42:19,390 --> 01:42:23,190
負責你懂的很多 那是家族的特點
You know about responsibility. It's a family trait.

986
01:42:23,260 --> 01:42:26,630
鄧肯家族的人都是負責的佼佼者 至少表面上是
Duncans are big in that department, at least on the surface.

987
01:42:26,730 --> 01:42:27,890
這不公平！
That's not fair!

988
01:42:28,000 --> 01:42:31,360
我不認為我們有責任感有什麼錯誤
I don't think it's wrong to feel a sense of duty.

989
01:42:31,430 --> 01:42:35,700
有時候你說話時眉毛一揚
Sometimes, when you turn the exact same phrase...

990
01:42:35,770 --> 01:42:38,210
那種口氣
...Iift an eyebrow in the exact same way...

991
01:42:38,270 --> 01:42:40,610
那種動作
...I see and I hear your father.

992
01:42:40,680 --> 01:42:42,440
跟你父親一模一樣！
The two of you, one!

993
01:42:42,510 --> 01:42:46,850
就像是棵小樹在一棵大樹的樹蔭下 受到庇護一樣
Like a big tree and a little tree in its shade, where the acorn fell.

994
01:42:46,920 --> 01:42:52,220
羅傑，我到你面前來 是因為我認為你需要我
Roger, I came over here to you because I thought you might need me.

995
01:42:56,630 --> 01:42:58,030
現在…
Right now...

996
01:42:59,230 --> 01:43:02,200
我最需要的是…是這個
what I need most...is this.

997
01:43:07,100 --> 01:43:10,330
我向自己保證 如果再見到你
I promised myself if I ever saw you again,

998
01:43:10,410 --> 01:43:11,900
我一定向你坦白一切
I'd make a full confession.

999
01:43:11,980 --> 01:43:14,270
謝謝你，不用了
No, but thank you.

1000
01:43:14,340 --> 01:43:16,740
可是你一點兒也不瞭解我
-But you don't know anything about me.

1001
01:43:16,810 --> 01:43:18,300
我瞭解你
-But I do.

1002
01:43:18,350 --> 01:43:20,280
你身無分文
You're penniless...

1003
01:43:20,350 --> 01:43:23,510
你在法國南方沒有別墅
...you have no villa in the south of France...

1004
01:43:23,590 --> 01:43:26,580
沒有古董，沒有名畫
...no antiques coming, no paintings.

1005
01:43:26,660 --> 01:43:28,820
不過，我不在乎
But, Harlee, I don't care.

1006
01:43:31,190 --> 01:43:34,720
我是個卑鄙小人.華而不實的騙子
I'm a cheap tinhorn. A two-bit con man.

1007
01:43:34,830 --> 01:43:38,290
你不卑鄙，只是不夠成功
Not cheap. Maybe unsuccessful.

1008
01:43:38,400 --> 01:43:40,840
我知道你不是成心的
But you see, your heart isn't in it.

1009
01:43:40,900 --> 01:43:43,460
你騙了人心堣]不好受…
How can you cheat people effectively...

1010
01:43:43,540 --> 01:43:45,840
好怎麼能假的像呢？
...if you don't enjoy cheating them?

1011
01:43:45,910 --> 01:43:48,780
我今天帶你來想買你1000股
I came here to sell you 1 000 shares

1012
01:43:48,850 --> 01:43:50,900
阿納海姆公司股票
in Greater Anaheim Power and Light!

1013
01:43:50,980 --> 01:43:52,680
那是一筆好投資嗎？
Is it a good investment?

1014
01:43:52,750 --> 01:43:55,340
根本沒有阿納海姆公司
There is no Greater Anaheim Power and Light.

1015
01:43:55,420 --> 01:43:57,580
只有我自己印的證書
Only the certificate I had printed.

1016
01:43:57,650 --> 01:44:00,280
我要說你一定很欣賞這古董
I think you'd have admired the artwork.

1017
01:44:00,360 --> 01:44:01,880
多精美的雕刻
Beautiful engraving.

1018
01:44:01,960 --> 01:44:03,590
我想看看
I'd like to see it.

1019
01:44:05,360 --> 01:44:06,730
在我上衣口袋
It's in my jacket.

1020
01:44:06,800 --> 01:44:10,100
我把它脫了 扔在了別的地方
I took the jacket off. It was needed elsewhere.

1021
01:44:10,170 --> 01:44:11,790
你看我說的是什麼？
You see what I mean?

1022
01:44:11,870 --> 01:44:15,030
我甚至不能給你一張偽造的股票證書
I can't even deliver a phony stock certificate.

1023
01:44:18,810 --> 01:44:20,470
聽見我說的話了嗎？
Did you hear what I said?

1024
01:44:22,110 --> 01:44:23,740
聽見了
Every word.

1025
01:44:24,950 --> 01:44:28,780
那你告訴我你很震驚 至少是很失望
Then tell me you're shocked or at least disappointed.

1026
01:44:28,850 --> 01:44:31,580
- 可我沒有 - 別否認！
-But I'm not. -You must be!

1027
01:44:31,650 --> 01:44:33,710
我沒有，哈瑞
Harlee, I'm not.

1028
01:44:38,930 --> 01:44:40,120
好啊
Okey

1029
01:44:49,910 --> 01:44:51,400
我去去就來
I'll be right back.

1030
01:44:52,810 --> 01:44:55,470
我和道格說幾句，好嗎
Give me a few minutes with Doug, will you, dear?

1031
01:44:55,550 --> 01:44:56,840
當然
Sure.

1032
01:45:08,020 --> 01:45:09,580
威爾.吉丁斯死了
Will Giddings is dead.

1033
01:45:12,300 --> 01:45:13,960
他20分鐘前死的
He died 20 minutes ago.

1034
01:45:19,340 --> 01:45:20,930
天?
Oh, boy.

1035
01:45:23,940 --> 01:45:28,140
誰知道天亮前還會死多少人
I wonder how many more will be dead tomorrow?

1036
01:45:28,210 --> 01:45:30,180
我總以為我們蓋的樓…
I thought we were building something...

1037
01:45:30,250 --> 01:45:33,740
能讓人們在堶惘w全的工作和生活！
...where people could work, live and be safe.

1038
01:45:33,820 --> 01:45:35,250
如果你要削減成本
If you had to cut costs

1039
01:45:35,320 --> 01:45:37,810
幹嘛不減掉幾層樓？
why didn't you cut floors instead of corners?

1040
01:45:39,260 --> 01:45:41,080
你聽著 
Now listen.

1041
01:45:41,080 --> 01:45:43,790
我是決定…
Any decisions that were made for

1042
01:45:43,790 --> 01:45:46,520
更換了一些建材…
the use of alternate building materials. .

1043
01:45:46,630 --> 01:45:50,620
這麼做是因為我是建材商 我有權作決定…
...were made because l, as a builder, have a right to make those decisions.

1044
01:45:50,730 --> 01:45:54,260
只要我符合標準 可是，我深信我已經做到了這一點！
If I remain within the building code, and goddamn it, I did!

1045
01:45:54,340 --> 01:45:56,460
還是老一套，建築標準
Oh, here we go again!

1046
01:45:56,540 --> 01:45:58,100
建築標準
The building code. Come on.

1047
01:45:58,170 --> 01:46:00,840
每次有麻煩你總是拿它當藉口
That's a standard cop-out when you're in trouble!

1048
01:46:00,910 --> 01:46:03,170
我從通風管道爬過來
I was crawling around up there.

1049
01:46:03,250 --> 01:46:05,650
那些材料都不是阻燒材料！
The duct holes weren't fire-stopped!

1050
01:46:05,720 --> 01:46:09,280
走廊堥S有防火門
Corridors without fire doors and the sprinklers won't work.

1051
01:46:09,350 --> 01:46:12,410
電力系統又有什麼用呢？
And an electrical system that's good for what?

1052
01:46:12,490 --> 01:46:14,720
我看只能引起火災
I mean, it's good for starting fires!

1053
01:46:16,060 --> 01:46:18,580
當時我又在哪？
Where was I when all this was going on?

1054
01:46:18,690 --> 01:46:22,530
我也有罪 我和你跟你那該死的女婿一樣
Because I'm just as guilty as you and that goddamn son-in-law of yours!

1055
01:46:24,100 --> 01:46:27,070
害死人的人該叫什麼？
What do they call it when you kill people?

1056
01:46:38,410 --> 01:46:40,010
小心，往上噴

1057
01:46:47,720 --> 01:46:49,950
- 是誰？ - 是隊長
-Who is it? -Chief O'Hallorhan.

1058
01:46:50,030 --> 01:46:51,360
出什麼事了？
-What happened?

1059
01:46:51,460 --> 01:46:55,230
中央走廊發生爆炸 我們已經發出第五次警報
-Part of the central corridor just blew. We've got in the fifth alarm.

1060
01:46:55,300 --> 01:46:57,730
直升機呢
The helicopters?

1061
01:46:57,800 --> 01:46:59,170
風太大了，他們無法降落
It's too windy.

1062
01:46:59,240 --> 01:47:02,730
所以我們想在舞廳和 皮爾斯大廈之間拉一條吊索
We'll set up the breeches buoy on the Peerless Building.

1063
01:47:03,910 --> 01:47:05,500
需要我們做什麼
What can we do to help?

1064
01:47:05,580 --> 01:47:08,770
把窗戶邊所有易燃物都搬開
Move your combustible material away from the window.

1065
01:47:09,980 --> 01:47:11,310
好的，明白了
Okay, gotcha.

1066
01:47:25,130 --> 01:47:28,120
- 沒有在窗簾 - 好的，讓我們把它扯下來
There's nobody on those drapes. Let's get them.

1067
01:47:28,230 --> 01:47:30,060
你們過來
Jake, give me a hand.

1068
01:48:09,470 --> 01:48:12,530
- 找到她了？ - 電話都不通啊
Did you reach her?The phones are all out.

1069
01:48:13,710 --> 01:48:16,700
再等一會兒 我們就能回家了
Just a little while longer, and we'll all be home together.

1070
01:48:18,180 --> 01:48:21,120
能和她說下幾句話就好了
If only I could have talked to her.

1071
01:48:21,180 --> 01:48:23,520
讓她知道我們在想她…
Let her know we were thinking of her.

1072
01:48:25,550 --> 01:48:29,580
告訴她… 她是我們的寶貝女兒
Told her how precious she is to us.

1073
01:48:34,060 --> 01:48:36,220
她還是個孩子
She's still such a child.

1074
01:48:37,600 --> 01:48:39,030
她甚至不知道…
She doesn't even know

1075
01:48:39,100 --> 01:48:41,830
我把保險箱的鑰匙放在哪
where I keep the key to the safety deposit box.

1076
01:48:41,900 --> 01:48:43,840
她怎麼開呢？
How will she be able to get into it?

1077
01:48:46,380 --> 01:48:47,900
我是說…
I mean...

1078
01:48:49,280 --> 01:48:50,770
需要的時候
...if she should have to.

1079
01:48:54,520 --> 01:48:56,380
別胡思亂想了
The things you think of.

1080
01:48:57,850 --> 01:48:59,340
能幫我一把嗎？
Do you wanna help me?

1081
01:49:06,800 --> 01:49:08,230
好的
-Here he is. -The wind's down a little.

1082
01:49:08,300 --> 01:49:11,490
隊長，現在風小了點 我們想試試降落
We're gonna try for a landing.

1083
01:49:12,600 --> 01:49:14,260
接通羅伯茨，我要和他通話
Get Roberts.

1084
01:49:19,910 --> 01:49:22,340
- 是我 - 讓十個人上樓頂
Get 10 people on the roof.

1085
01:49:22,410 --> 01:49:25,900
其餘的十人一組 我們開始準備空運
Have the rest stand by.We're gonna start airlifting.

1086
01:49:26,020 --> 01:49:27,610
我的
Will do.

1087
01:49:31,490 --> 01:49:34,180
把這些放到那 有的時候好拿
Put these over there.

1088
01:49:34,260 --> 01:49:37,950
給我一打紙和一支筆 再拿一個白蘭地酒杯
Give me a pad of paper and a pencil.Give me that brandy snifter too.

1089
01:49:38,030 --> 01:49:41,090
- 他們準備降落？ - 他們想試一試
-Doug, are they going to land? -They're gonna try.

1090
01:49:41,160 --> 01:49:44,390
我們先送孩子 然後是婦女
We'll send the kids out first, then the women.

1091
01:49:44,470 --> 01:49:47,060
在紙上寫信號 100個左右
Number these up to 100 or so.

1092
01:49:47,140 --> 01:49:48,660
摩天樓輪盤賭
High-rise roulette.

1093
01:49:48,740 --> 01:49:51,000
摩天樓輪盤賭 說得對
High-rise roulette. That's right.

1094
01:49:51,110 --> 01:49:53,910
道格，我不再有機會告訴你
-There may not be time to tell you -There will be.

1095
01:49:56,180 --> 01:49:57,740
去通知他們
I'll go tell everybody.

1096
01:49:57,850 --> 01:50:00,480
你寫好後，讓他們抓鬮
Pass those out when you're ready.

1097
01:50:27,550 --> 01:50:30,880
記住上面風很大 尤其是直升機下降時
There'll be a lot of wind up there,

1098
01:50:30,950 --> 01:50:32,710
大家要待在一起，別散開
so everybody stay in one group. Come on.

1099
01:50:49,630 --> 01:50:51,430
靠後！靠後！
Stay back, stay back!

1100
01:50:57,010 --> 01:50:58,130
小心！
Look out!

1101
01:51:42,150 --> 01:51:44,020
羅伯茨，羅伯茨
Roberts! Roberts!

1102
01:51:44,090 --> 01:51:46,820
隊長要找你講話
Chief O'Hallorhan wants to speak to you.

1103
01:51:46,890 --> 01:51:50,230
讓一下 對不起，讓我們過去！
All right, make way. Coming through, coming through!

1104
01:51:55,270 --> 01:51:56,790
他來了
Here he is now.

1105
01:51:59,370 --> 01:52:00,360
聽著
Yeah

1106
01:52:00,440 --> 01:52:03,700
聽著，羅伯茨，我知道飛行員死了
Roberts, I know those pilots are dead, and l--

1107
01:52:03,810 --> 01:52:06,110
上面一片混亂
God, it was just awful up there.

1108
01:52:07,780 --> 01:52:10,580
現在吊索是我們最大的希望
Listen, our best chance now is the breeches buoy.

1109
01:52:10,650 --> 01:52:13,310
讓我的那兩個人打破玻璃窗
I told my two firemen to knock out a window.

1110
01:52:13,390 --> 01:52:15,880
從直升飛機上給你們發射一根繩子
We'll try to shoot a line from a chopper.

1111
01:52:16,760 --> 01:52:17,980
好的
Okey

1112
01:52:23,600 --> 01:52:26,160
你們誰帶剪刀了嗎？
Hey, one of you guys got a pair of clippers?

1113
01:52:26,230 --> 01:52:29,760
- 我有，要它幹什麼？ - 我得想個辦法
-Sure, what do you want them for? -I want to try something.

1114
01:52:42,680 --> 01:52:45,120
消防隊員要打破玻璃窗 為了安全，請大家後退
Step back. The firemen are gonna knock out the windows.

1115
01:52:46,150 --> 01:52:47,580
請大家後退一些
Step back and you won't get hurt.

1116
01:54:39,790 --> 01:54:41,720
大家靜靜，請聽我說？
May I have your attention, please?

1117
01:54:43,490 --> 01:54:46,520
我們起動了一台外面的引力電梯
We've activated a gravity brake on that outside elevator.

1118
01:54:46,600 --> 01:54:49,900
它沒有足夠的動力再上來 但至少能把12個人送下去
There's no power to bring it back up, but at least we can get 12 people out.

1119
01:54:49,970 --> 01:54:51,630
哪12個？
Which 12?

1120
01:54:51,740 --> 01:54:55,670
剛才那十個上樓頂的 再加上兩個
The same group that was up on the roof and two additions.

1121
01:54:55,770 --> 01:54:57,740
救孩子的那名女士和消防員…
The woman who saved the children's lives and a fireman!

1122
01:54:57,840 --> 01:55:00,710
我要一個受過訓練的人
I want a trained man in there.

1123
01:55:02,910 --> 01:55:04,810
你去吧，快點上電梯吧
All right, let's move it out!

1124
01:55:12,920 --> 01:55:16,790
瑪姬，給你，拿著這個 你就可以走了
Marge!Take this. Take it! You can get out! Go on.

1125
01:55:16,860 --> 01:55:18,690
你在做什麼？
What are you doing?

1126
01:55:20,960 --> 01:55:22,300
對不起
I'm sorry.

1127
01:55:26,200 --> 01:55:28,690
我要你離開這兒
I want you out of here.

1128
01:55:28,770 --> 01:55:32,000
那樣的話你就不用擔心我了？ 難道我在下面就不會擔心你嗎？
So you can stop worrying about me? What about me worrying about you?

1129
01:55:32,080 --> 01:55:35,340
那樣你才能幫助我 親愛的，幫幫我
It's the only way you can help me.Help me.

1130
01:55:48,260 --> 01:55:52,020
如果…如果你讓我去北極
If you asked me to go to the North Pole...

1131
01:55:52,100 --> 01:55:55,900
或者是荒無人煙的沙漠，我答應你
...or even the cliffs of Mendocino, I'd go.

1132
01:55:55,970 --> 01:55:58,060
我明天向你提出，怎麼樣？
What if I ask you tomorrow?

1133
01:56:08,350 --> 01:56:09,710
請吧
Please.

1134
01:56:13,480 --> 01:56:16,150
- 夫人，我來抱她 - 謝謝你
-Ma'am, I'll take her. -Thank you.

1135
01:56:16,220 --> 01:56:18,050
- 跟我來，菲力浦 - 好的
Come on, Phillip.

1136
01:56:20,660 --> 01:56:23,420
以後我再也不會讓你離開我了
I'll never let you go anywhere without me again.

1137
01:56:23,490 --> 01:56:26,520
我再也不想離開你，親愛的
I don't want to.Ever again.

1138
01:56:30,270 --> 01:56:32,760
- 我去大堂找你 - 我等你
-I'll meet you in the lobby. -I'll be waiting.

1139
01:56:32,840 --> 01:56:35,240
還有一位女士沒到
We're still a lady short.

1140
01:56:35,310 --> 01:56:37,830
- 你一定要走 - 可我不想離開你
-You've gotta go. -I don't want to leave you.

1141
01:56:37,940 --> 01:56:40,600
親愛的，我不會有事的 我向你保證
Honey, I'll make it. I promise you.

1142
01:56:40,680 --> 01:56:42,910
我有說謊，不算數的時候嗎？
Have I ever broken a promise to you?

1143
01:56:46,420 --> 01:56:47,910
祝你好運，親愛的
Good luck, honey.

1144
01:56:49,250 --> 01:56:50,480
請吧
Please.

1145
01:56:51,920 --> 01:56:53,480
準備好了嗎？
All set, everyone?

1146
01:57:02,830 --> 01:57:04,660
好了，我們走
Okay, here we go.

1147
01:58:46,970 --> 01:58:48,800
好了
Out of sight!

1148
01:58:50,610 --> 01:58:52,580
它們來了
Yeah, it's coming.

1149
01:58:52,680 --> 01:58:56,670
拽住繩子！ 往里拉！
Let's untie this, take it off, pull in the rest of the line!

1150
01:59:12,400 --> 01:59:13,830
抓緊它！拴緊往里拉
All right, hold it right there!

1151
01:59:13,900 --> 01:59:16,460
抓住主纜繩
Bring in another 20 feet of that main line.

1152
01:59:16,530 --> 01:59:17,900
抓緊
Hold on

1153
01:59:26,410 --> 01:59:27,780
就這樣
That's it.

1154
01:59:29,450 --> 01:59:32,070
往娷I
All right, bring in a little more!

1155
01:59:32,150 --> 01:59:34,140
來幫一下
That's it. Hold it now. Brace yourselves.

1156
01:59:41,590 --> 01:59:43,150
當心頭
Watch your heads!

1157
01:59:46,760 --> 01:59:49,290
拉呀，再往堣@點
Grab it! Take it back and secure it!

1158
01:59:51,900 --> 01:59:55,600
好了，先別拉
All right, let it go!Let it go!

1159
01:59:55,710 --> 01:59:57,700
栓好了
All right, go on! Take it out!

1160
02:00:11,120 --> 02:00:12,680
找個地方固定住
Okay, take ahold.

1161
02:00:23,470 --> 02:00:25,530
主纜繩系好了沒有，保險嗎
How about the main line? Secured?

1162
02:00:25,640 --> 02:00:26,900
好
Good!

1163
02:01:16,950 --> 02:01:18,110
隊長
Chief!

1164
02:01:22,230 --> 02:01:26,320
110層發生爆炸，觀光電梯脫離軌道
Explosion above 110 blew the elevator off its track.

1165
02:01:26,400 --> 02:01:27,890
只靠一根剛纜吊著
It's hanging by a cable.

1166
02:01:31,070 --> 02:01:34,770
- 上面有多少人？ - 滿的，差不多12個
-How many people in it? -Loaded. I'd say about 12.

1167
02:01:41,450 --> 02:01:43,040
你打算怎麼辦
What're you gonna go?

1168
02:01:49,990 --> 02:01:51,080
弗萊克
Flaker.

1169
02:01:52,320 --> 02:01:54,290
- 弗萊克 - 我在
-Flaker! -Sir?

1170
02:01:56,360 --> 02:01:59,190
能不能給我一架帶絞盤個剛纜的直升機
Can you give me a chopper with a winch and some cable?

1171
02:01:59,260 --> 02:02:02,250
送我到皮爾斯大廈樓頂去
Have them pick me up on the Peerless Building.

1172
02:02:02,330 --> 02:02:04,770
- 我們去準備 - 好的
Got it.

1173
02:02:07,470 --> 02:02:09,840
我上去用鉤子鉤住電梯
Try and get a hitch on that elevator.

1174
02:02:09,910 --> 02:02:12,430
用直升飛機把它鉤到地面
Drop it down to the deck by the chopper.

1175
02:02:22,250 --> 02:02:23,880
媽媽，媽媽
Mommy, Mommy!

1176
02:02:33,860 --> 02:02:36,260
你不哭我也不哭
I won't cry if you won't cry.

1177
02:03:26,720 --> 02:03:29,450
好了，放開她
Okay, let her go!

1178
02:03:32,060 --> 02:03:33,550
當心下面
Look out below!

1179
02:03:52,380 --> 02:03:54,740
好了，把它拉過來
All right! There's one in there!

1180
02:03:54,810 --> 02:03:56,570
拉呀
Come on! Pull it in!

1181
02:04:05,920 --> 02:04:09,920
鉤住那把椅子
All right, let's haul that chair in! Come on!

1182
