-I can't!

1190
02:04:38,520 --> 02:04:40,150
沒事的
-Yes, you can.

1191
02:04:40,220 --> 02:04:44,130
別鬆手，別讓我掉下去
Oh, God! Don't let go of me!Don't let go of me! Don't let me fall!

1192
02:04:46,130 --> 02:04:48,260
別鬆手
Don't let go!

1193
02:04:49,430 --> 02:04:53,100
不要，別鬆手
Don't let go of me!

1194
02:04:56,010 --> 02:04:57,410
好的

1195
02:05:16,560 --> 02:05:18,860
好了，到了

1196
02:05:18,930 --> 02:05:21,900
好了，放下那把椅子

1197
02:05:21,970 --> 02:05:23,900
沒事的夫人，到了

1198
02:05:26,540 --> 02:05:28,700
別鬆手
Get me out, please! Hold it right there.

1199
02:05:38,680 --> 02:05:40,710
好了，放下纜繩
Okay, lower the cable.

1200
02:05:46,090 --> 02:05:48,720
抓住鉤子，抓穩
Grab that hook!Steady.

1201
02:05:51,190 --> 02:05:54,600
帶燈了嗎
What about the torch?Lash it tight.

1202
02:06:00,340 --> 02:06:01,700
我是奧霍羅漢
-This is O'Hallorhan.

1203
02:06:01,810 --> 02:06:03,800
聽見了，隊長
-We read you, chief.

1204
02:06:03,910 --> 02:06:06,340
我要你把我個鉤子…
Pick me up with the hook...

1205
02:06:06,440 --> 02:06:09,500
送到觀光電梯的頂上
...and set me down on the scenic elevator.

1206
02:06:09,580 --> 02:06:11,710
你先把電梯吊起來…
Then you'll pick up the elevator

1207
02:06:11,780 --> 02:06:15,050
慢慢的送到地上
and gently set it down on the street.

1208
02:06:15,120 --> 02:06:17,050
你能承受這重量嗎
Can you handle the weight?

1209
02:06:17,120 --> 02:06:20,650
我想我能行
I think we can handle it. We'll find out in a hurry.

1210
02:06:21,790 --> 02:06:22,920
好
Okey

1211
02:06:41,310 --> 02:06:42,470
鉤住
Watch it!

1212
02:06:45,580 --> 02:06:46,880
好
Okey

1213
02:06:47,750 --> 02:06:49,240
出發
Take it away!

1214
02:07:18,780 --> 02:07:20,770
我們還有多長時間
How much time do we have?

1215
02:07:23,620 --> 02:07:25,350
我也不知道
I wish I knew.

1216
02:07:25,420 --> 02:07:28,020
見鬼，這樓不是你蓋的嗎
Goddamn it, Jim, you built the place!

1217
02:07:34,100 --> 02:07:37,400
