I just don't think that all of us are gonna make it.

1218
02:08:34,990 --> 02:08:37,150
下一個該我了
Well, I guess I'm next.

1219
02:08:37,230 --> 02:08:39,750
你一定不允許我留在這
I don't suppose you'll let me stay.

1220
02:08:43,700 --> 02:08:45,670
好吧，回頭見
Come on. I'll see you soon.

1221
02:08:54,540 --> 02:08:55,980
我愛你
I love you.

1222
02:08:59,980 --> 02:09:01,610
放繩子
Let it go!

1223
02:09:58,840 --> 02:10:00,570
它能經得住嗎
You think this'll hold it?

1224
02:10:00,640 --> 02:10:03,370
希望能，我們得割斷電梯剛纜
It'd better. We have to cut the elevator cable.

1225
02:10:12,590 --> 02:10:14,820
- 你多少號？
-What's your number? -68.

1226
02:10:14,890 --> 02:10:16,260
我是47
47.

1227
02:12:44,970 --> 02:12:46,570
快到了

1228
02:13:03,230 --> 02:13:05,290
拉姆齊夫人，到了
Here, Mrs. Ramsay,

1229
02:13:05,360 --> 02:13:07,120
你沒事了
you'll be all right now.

1230
02:13:07,200 --> 02:13:08,250
請幫我個忙好嗎
-You'll be all right.

1231
02:13:08,330 --> 02:13:10,860
請告訴我丈夫我沒事
-Tell my husband I'm all right.

1232
02:13:10,930 --> 02:13:13,600
- 告訴他我沒事了 - 我會的
-Tell him I'll be all right. -I will.

1233
02:13:13,700 --> 02:13:16,300
我會等著他
-And I'll see him at home later.

1234
02:13:16,410 --> 02:13:18,400
我一定告訴他
-I will.

1235
02:13:18,510 --> 02:13:19,910
該走了
Let's go.

1236
02:13:28,800 --> 02:13:29,270
她沒事了
Oh, my God, you're all right!

1237
02:13:33,490 --> 02:13:35,120
小心梯子
Watch the ladder.

1238
02:13:41,340 --> 02:13:42,730
讓開

1239
02:14:20,010 --> 02:14:23,030
嗨，邁克，副局長在叫你
Hey, Mike deputy wants to see you.

1240
02:14:35,690 --> 02:14:37,490
邁克，，我們研究了…
Mike, we've been checking

1241
02:14:37,560 --> 02:14:39,360
樓頂舞廳的情況
the situation in the Promenade Room.

1242
02:14:39,430 --> 02:14:43,020
我們認為他們只剩下17到18分鐘
We figure they've got 17 or 18 minutes left, if that.

1243
02:14:43,100 --> 02:14:46,530
用吊索把所有的人運下來需要三小時
It'll take more than 3 hours to get them down by breeches buoy.

1244
02:14:46,600 --> 02:14:49,160
如果不採取行動他們就會死
They'll die up there if something's not done.

1245
02:14:49,240 --> 02:14:50,900
我們有辦法
We might have the answer.

1246
02:14:50,970 --> 02:14:52,770
詹森先生是結構工程師
Johnson's a structural engineer.

1247
02:14:52,870 --> 02:14:54,810
告訴隊長你的計算結果
Tell the chief your calculations.

1248
02:14:54,910 --> 02:14:58,140
根據我的觀點
The structural strength of the joists in that room...

1249
02:14:58,210 --> 02:15:01,080
頂樓舞廳結構和支架的 承重力肯定能頂住爆破
...could definitely withstand the explosion.

1250
02:15:03,280 --> 02:15:04,510
什麼爆破
What explosion?

1251
