隊長直升機準備好了 在廣場上
Chief, we've got the copter ready.Wait a minute.

1252
02:15:10,090 --> 02:15:12,060
這件事我來處理 你回去幹你的工作吧
We'll handle that. Just get back to your job.

1253
02:15:14,530 --> 02:15:16,020
好的，先生
Yes, sir.

1254
02:15:18,300 --> 02:15:19,530
什麼爆破
What explosion?

1255
02:15:19,600 --> 02:15:23,000
我們可以將舞廳上面的蓄水池炸開
We can blow the tanks two floors above the Promenade Room.

1256
02:15:23,070 --> 02:15:26,510
那堶惘酗@百萬加侖水足以把大火撲滅
They hold 1,000,000 gallons of water. That's enough to drown the fire.

1257
02:15:30,510 --> 02:15:33,040
- 你瘋了 - 這是唯一的辦法
-You're crazy. -Mike, it's the only way.

1258
02:15:33,150 --> 02:15:37,050
你怎麼知道有效 你會把人都殺死
You could kill everybody up there.

1259
02:15:37,120 --> 02:15:38,680
我不這麼想
I don't think so.

1260
02:15:38,750 --> 02:15:40,650
你沒有想
You don't think?

1261
02:15:40,720 --> 02:15:44,320
我們內計算了壓力負荷因數以及
When you take into account the stress factors, the design--

1262
02:15:44,390 --> 02:15:46,420
好了，等一下
Wait a minute. Just hold it.

1263
02:15:46,490 --> 02:15:48,990
沒必要說那麼多了，邁克 我們已經做出了決定
We've already made the decision.

1264
02:15:49,060 --> 02:15:52,900
現在需要一個人上去裝炸藥並引爆
Someone has got to go up there, rig the charges and blow them.

1265
02:15:52,970 --> 02:15:57,600
局堨u有兩個人能勝任，你和康納斯
There's only two people qualified for that. You and Conners.

1266
02:15:57,670 --> 02:15:59,870
他們剛把康納斯送下來
They just brought Conners down.

1267
02:15:59,970 --> 02:16:02,840
正去燒傷醫院的路上
He's on his way to the burn center.

1268
02:16:02,940 --> 02:16:07,110
在目前這種情況下 我不能命令你上去
Under the circumstances, we can't order you to go up there.

1269
02:16:07,180 --> 02:16:10,840
我只能告訴你實情
I'm just laying it out for you.

1270
02:16:10,920 --> 02:16:13,220
由你自己…
But you... .

1271
02:16:13,290 --> 02:16:15,380
你明白是嗎？
You see how it is, don't you?

1272
02:16:19,290 --> 02:16:21,320
那我怎麼回來了
How do I get back down?

1273
02:16:27,300 --> 02:16:28,890
盡說些廢話
Oh, shit!

1274
02:16:56,130 --> 02:16:57,620
女人全都走了
The women are gone.

1275
02:16:58,900 --> 02:17:00,630
下面該輪到我們了
We are going next.

1276
02:17:12,680 --> 02:17:17,450
你們都有號碼 你們必須按號碼走
You've all got numbers.And you're gonna take your turn.

1277
02:17:17,520 --> 02:17:19,850
如果能給大家一些安慰的話…
And if it's any consolation...

1278
02:17:23,120 --> 02:17:27,190
我將最後一個離開這 跟我女婿在一起
...I'll be the last one out of here along with my son-in-law.

1279
02:17:36,770 --> 02:17:37,830
羅伯茨

1280
02:17:37,910 --> 02:17:40,870
火已經失控 正朝你們燒過去
It's out of control. And it's coming your way.

1281
02:17:43,710 --> 02:17:45,910
你們也許只有15分鐘
You got about 15 minutes.

1282
02:17:47,580 --> 02:17:49,520
他們想了個辦法
Now, they want to try something.

1283
02:17:49,580 --> 02:17:52,250
他們想炸開你們頭上的蓄水池…
They wanna blow those water tanks above you.

1284
02:17:52,320 --> 02:17:53,950
也許能把火澆滅
They think it'll kill the fire.

1285
02:18:01,700 --> 02:18:03,990
你們怎麼能把炸彈運上來
How are they gonna get the explosives up here?

1286
02:18:05,830 --> 02:18:09,130
他們要找個該死的蠢貨運上去
They'll find some dumb son of a bitch to bring it up.

1287
02:18:16,680 --> 02:18:18,200
等等，我告訴他們
Hang on, I'll tell them.

1288
02:18:23,250 --> 02:18:27,350
他們想打開我們頭上的蓄水池把火澆滅
They want to put out the fire by blowing the water tanks above us.

1289
02:18:27,420 --> 02:18:29,480
那就意味著大量的水，鋼筋和混凝土
We'll eat a lot of water and concrete,

1290
02:18:29,560 --> 02:18:34,020
如果他們不試試 我們都會被燒焦的
but if they don't try it, we'll burn.The fire's out of control.

1291
02:18:34,100 --> 02:18:37,590
我們只有15分鐘
They think we got maybe 15 minutes.

1292
02:18:37,670 --> 02:18:41,070
也許我們有人能活下去 沒有選擇了
This way, some of us might survive. We got no options.

1293
02:18:48,240 --> 02:18:50,680
快，我們走
Come on. Let's go.

1294
02:18:54,080 --> 02:18:55,640
抓住繩子
Get that line.

1295
02:19:04,690 --> 02:19:05,660
下來
Get off!

1296
02:19:06,830 --> 02:19:08,950
你瘋了，拉住繩子
-You crazy bastards! Drop this line! -Let go of me!

1297
02:19:09,030 --> 02:19:11,260
- 放開！ - 會斷的
Drop the line. It's not gonna work.

1298
02:19:12,030 --> 02:19:15,520
吊索承受不起這個重力
It won't hold everybody!

1299
02:19:16,970 --> 02:19:18,870
下來
Get off!

1300
02:19:19,510 --> 02:19:21,370
下來
Get off!

1301
02:19:21,440 --> 02:19:23,930
走開
-Get the hell out of there!

1302
02:19:27,350 --> 02:19:29,150
不，不
-Go!

1303
02:19:32,190 --> 02:19:33,780
下來
Get off.

1304
02:19:44,630 --> 02:19:45,720
隊長
Chief.

1305
02:19:47,970 --> 02:19:49,560
是我

1306
02:19:49,640 --> 02:19:51,660
吊索已經不存在了
We lost the breeches buoy.

1307
02:19:51,740 --> 02:19:54,500
這媯o生了騷亂 不過已經過去了
It was panic up here.It's under control now.

1308
02:19:56,080 --> 02:19:58,340
直升機將把我送到樓頂
I'll try and set down on the roof.

1309
02:19:58,410 --> 02:20:00,310
我需要你的幫助
I'll need you up there.

1310
02:20:00,380 --> 02:20:04,820
我知道該在哪放炸藥 但我不會安
I know where to place the charges, but I don't know how.

1311
02:20:04,890 --> 02:20:06,580
我懂
I know how.

1312
02:20:09,220 --> 02:20:10,780
好的

1313
02:20:10,860 --> 02:20:12,490
樓上見
See you up there.

1314
02:20:20,400 --> 02:20:23,300
想辦法把自己固定住
You'll have to tie yourselves down.

1315
02:20:23,370 --> 02:20:26,200
用桌布，繩子，皮帶，找到什麼用什麼
Ropes, tablecloths, belts,anything you can find!

1316
02:20:37,750 --> 02:20:41,350
我的上帝啊.別把自己跟玻璃捆在一起
For God's sakes, Carlos. Don't tie yourself up to a lot of glass.

1317
02:20:41,420 --> 02:20:42,910
那是29年的陳酒
That's the '29.

1318
02:21:26,400 --> 02:21:27,660
試試
Try it.

1319
02:21:29,670 --> 02:21:31,100
很好
It's okay.

1320
02:21:36,910 --> 02:21:38,170
道格…
Doug...

1321
02:21:39,550 --> 02:21:42,340
我沒想到會發生這樣的事情
...I never thought this could happen.

1322
02:21:42,420 --> 02:21:43,540
我知道
Sure.

1323
02:24:11,600 --> 02:24:13,190
嗨

1324
02:24:13,270 --> 02:24:15,200
我們還有多少時間
-How much time you think we got?

1325
02:24:15,270 --> 02:24:17,760
十分鐘 也許更少
-Ten minutes, maybe less.

1326
02:24:17,810 --> 02:24:21,240
炸水箱的同時 必須把樓板也炸穿
We'll have to blow the floors as well as the tanks, you know.

1327
02:24:22,240 --> 02:24:24,680
好吧，這是你的雷管
All right. This is your detonator.

1328
02:24:24,750 --> 02:24:27,240
你用瞬間引爆 我用延時引爆
You're running instantaneous. I'm running delayed. Here you go.

1329
02:24:27,350 --> 02:24:30,410
拿著，這是炸藥
This is your explosive.

1330
02:24:30,480 --> 02:24:31,970
這是計時器
This is the timer.

1331
02:24:32,050 --> 02:24:33,540
待會你拿出電線
Later on, after you throw the wire...

1332
02:24:33,590 --> 02:24:37,490
我們那它劈開插入電線 定好時就可以爆炸
...we'll plug it and splice it into the timer, set it, and it blows.

1333
02:24:40,860 --> 02:24:42,520
像這樣.
Set your explosive

1334
02:24:43,630 --> 02:24:44,720
定好炸藥
like this.

1335
02:24:49,100 --> 02:24:50,870
拿好雷管…
Take your detonator,

1336
02:24:50,940 --> 02:24:52,430
拔出插頭…
pull the plug.

1337
02:24:54,070 --> 02:24:55,230
把它扔了
Toss it.

1338
02:24:59,350 --> 02:25:00,370
會了嗎
-Got it?

1339
02:25:00,480 --> 02:25:01,570
會了
-I got it.

1340
02:26:15,660 --> 02:26:18,250
- 祝你好運，回頭見 - 好的，謝謝
-Good luck. See you later. -Okay, thanks.

1341
02:27:01,340 --> 02:27:02,730
給
Here you go.

1342
02:27:23,520 --> 02:27:26,720
- 你準備定幾分鐘？ - 5分鐘？
What will you set it for?Five.

1343
02:27:29,560 --> 02:27:31,290
我看來得及
I think we can make that.

1344
02:27:35,770 --> 02:27:37,070
好了
That's it.

1345
02:28:11,870 --> 02:28:14,170
快把自己捆下，快點笨蛋
Tie yourselves down, goddamn it!

1346
02:28:29,590 --> 02:28:31,180
沒有辦法穿過去
You'll never make it through there.

1347
02:28:31,260 --> 02:28:33,090
還剩多少時間
How much time?

1348
02:28:33,160 --> 02:28:34,420
3分鐘
Three and a half.

1349
02:28:35,660 --> 02:28:36,690
氧氣
Here.

1350
02:28:38,570 --> 02:28:39,730
給
Here.

1351
02:29:20,040 --> 02:29:21,410
我燒著了
I'm burning up!

1352
02:29:30,650 --> 02:29:31,950
快走
Let's go!

1353
02:29:38,690 --> 02:29:39,920
消防員
Fireman?

1354
02:33:21,920 --> 02:33:23,280
鮑勃
Bob!

1355
02:33:23,350 --> 02:33:24,610
鮑勃
Bob!

1356
02:33:25,890 --> 02:33:27,410
哦，天哪

1357
02:37:18,690 --> 02:37:21,620
對不起，她跟你在同一個電梯上
Excuse me.She was in the elevator with you.

1358
02:37:21,690 --> 02:37:23,750
一位漂亮的女士，米爾勒夫人
The fine-looking lady. Mrs. Mueller.

1359
02:37:23,820 --> 02:37:25,380
你看見了嗎
Have you seen her?

1360
02:37:27,730 --> 02:37:30,160
對不起，她死了
I'm sorry, she's dead.

1361
02:37:40,470 --> 02:37:41,630
利薩
Lisa!

1362
02:37:42,640 --> 02:37:43,700
利薩
Lisa!

1363
02:37:45,040 --> 02:37:46,240
利薩
Lisa!

1364
02:37:46,310 --> 02:37:48,010
- 克萊包尼 - 什麼？
-Claiborne! -What?

1365
02:38:39,770 --> 02:38:42,100
我不想讓你看到他
I didn't want you to see him.

1366
02:38:45,270 --> 02:38:48,760
我們誰也不能…
You know, there's nothing any of us

1367
02:38:48,880 --> 02:38:50,370
讓死人復活
can do to bring back the dead.

1368
02:38:59,520 --> 02:39:02,250
我只能乞求上帝
All I can do now is pray to God...

1369
02:39:04,290 --> 02:39:06,990
不要讓這種悲劇重演
...that I can stop this from ever happening again.

