02:39:46,600 --> 02:39:48,030
誰知道呢
I don't know.

1371
02:39:48,100 --> 02:39:51,630
也許應該留著它像現在這個樣子
Maybe they just ought to leave it the way it is.

1372
02:39:51,700 --> 02:39:54,640
作為警示後人的恥辱柱
Kind of a shrine to all the bullshit in the world.

1373
02:40:04,520 --> 02:40:08,040
今晚我們很幸運 死了不到200人
You know, we were lucky tonight. Body count's less than 200.

1374
02:40:09,320 --> 02:40:12,310
總有一天
One of these days,

1375
02:40:12,390 --> 02:40:14,380
火將使成千上萬的人喪命
they'll kill 1 0,000 in one of these firetraps.

1376
02:40:14,460 --> 02:40:18,120
我還將在延續的火苗中往外抬屍…
And I'll keep eating smoke and bringing out bodies...

1377
02:40:18,200 --> 02:40:20,530
直到有人問我…
...until somebody asks us...

1378
02:40:21,770 --> 02:40:23,630
該怎樣蓋樓
...how to build them.

1379
02:40:35,110 --> 02:40:38,050
好吧，我問你
Okay. I'm asking.

1380
02:40:39,720 --> 02:40:41,690
你能找到我
You know where to reach me.

1381
02:40:43,520 --> 02:40:45,010
再見，建築師
So long, architect.


